<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It would be nice to have addRow and removeRow  methods on rowsets so we can keep existing rowsets up to date.</p>

<p>Usage would be:</p>

<p>// Add row
$rowset-&gt;addRow($row);</p>

<p>// Remove row
$rowset-&gt;removeRow($row);</p>

